name: PDF Puzzle Ball Tutorial
description:
A puzzle ball looks amazing, is super fun, and now you can make it yourself!

Make it as a one-of-a-kind toy for your children, or make these as the perfect gifts for baby showers, birthdays, and other special occasions! You can customize each puzzle ball by choosing fabrics in your favourite colours, textures, and patterns!

Each PDF contains 14 pages of photos and easy-to-follow instructions. Templates are also included.

The finished ball is about 6 inches wide.

Your PDF will arrive as an email within 48 hours, so make sure that you have the correct email address listed with your account.  If you have any questions or if you would like a custom order, just contact me!

Have a great day!

name: PDF Pleated Pouch Tutorial
description:
This pleated pouch is perfectly adorable, and now you can make it yourself!

Make it as a one-of-a-kind wristlet for yourself, or make these as the perfect gifts for your friends! You can customize each pleated pouch to match your friend's personalities by choosing fabrics in their favourite colours and patterns!

Each PDF contains 20 pages of photos and easy-to-follow instructions. Templates are also included.

The finished pouch is 8.5 inches wide at the base and 5 3/4 inches tall. The upper band is 6 inches wide.

This is my favourite pouch to make for presents, and my friends have loved their pleated pouches!

If you have any questions or if you would like a custom order, just convo me!

Have a great day!
